<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>404 – Page Not Found</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Comic Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background: #fafafa; }
    .card {
      border: 2px solid #444;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 2em;
      margin: 5em auto;
      max-width: 400px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 2.3em;}
    .big { font-size: 4em; color: #4a76fd; font-weight: bold; }
    a { text-decoration: none; color: #4a76fd; font-weight: bold;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="big">404</div>
    <h2>Page Not Found</h2>
    <p>Sorry, the page you’re looking for doesn’t exist.</p>
    <a href="/home">← Go to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
